{"tid":1052424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖保祿補影相中六生無影 初中生稱教師告誡勿誇大事件","createTime":"2019-03-08T09:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T10:19:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1650b0544c86debde04d8990e694f016a95b60f","tid":1052424,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"聖保祿中學的「Last Day」報警風波引發公眾討論，校方今日(8日)安排「Last Day 2.0」讓中六學生回校補拍照片，但暫未見有該級學生回校的蹤影。有回校參加比賽的初中同學表示，班主任在事件過後曾向學生稱，「唔好信晒出面傳媒講嘅嘢，同叫我們不要將事件誇大」。<br />\n<br />\n該同學指，教師所說是擔心同學在社交媒體，用一些不好的說話去形容老師。對於老師就事件報警，同學表示，相信老師做事會有自己原因，可能有學生對老師的情緒較為偏激或激進，但她認為今日補拍與真正「Last day」的意義有所不同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%A5%BF%E8%A3%9C%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E5%BD%B1-%E5%88%9D%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AA%A1%E5%8B%BF%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-083931558.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2581%2596%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25A5%25BF%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E5%2588%259D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AA%25A1%25E5%258B%25BF%25E8%25AA%2587%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6-083931558.html&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=b7d533d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%96%E4%BF%9D%E7%A5%BF%E8%A3%9C%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E5%BD%B1-%E5%88%9D%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AA%A1%E5%8B%BF%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-083931558.html</a>"},{"pid":"e09f38b5a2e08f08fdc05c06935f7f27607905a5","tid":1052424,"uid":33099,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"隔住個mon 都聞到浸教畜味"},{"pid":"8d9148d8e854e7f25089c8f8627f21a5506a8c48","tid":1052424,"uid":19178,